ギター、ベースの練習とインタラクティブなレッスン

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 按照個人節奏，隨時學彈結他
一流の講師からギターを学ぼう

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Whether you’re a bona fide beginner or a seasoned master, Yousician can help you become a better musician. This invaluable resource guides you through thousands of songs packed with guitar and piano techniques like bends, slides, staccatos, and more. A sleek package, real-time feedback, and rewards-based courses make Yousician invaluable.

Bona fide beginner or seasoned master: Become a better musician with this invaluable resource that guides you through thousands of songs, packed with guitar and piano techniques, with motivational courses and real-time feedback.

Néophytes et pros, développez vos compétences musicales grâce à cette précieuse ressource qui vous guide à travers des milliers de morceaux étayés de techniques à la guitare ou au piano, avec des leçons motivantes et des retours en temps réel.

Bona fide beginner or seasoned master: become a better musician with this invaluable resource that guides you through thousands of songs, packed with guitar and piano techniques, with motivational courses and real-time feedback.
無論是真正的新手還是經驗豐富的大師，都能善用這項寶貴的資源成為更出色的音樂人，它會指導你演奏數千首歌曲，教授吉他和鋼琴演奏技巧，還會提供勵志課程和即時意見。
まったくの初心者も、熟練のミュージシャンも、優れた教材を集めたこのアプリで腕を磨きましょう。ギターやピアノの演奏テクニックを学べる何千もの楽曲を、やる気を促してくれるレッスンコースで、リアルタイムのフィードバックを受け取りながら練習できます。

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Learn guitar and piano with real-time feedback and rewards-based courses.
